{"tid":1407061,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論]0730鑽石山地鐵","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:18:56.000Z","uid":268237,"like":91,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1f6765381bc9b2153df9061a1f86a16de9297c","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"雖然小弟唔明點解唔要九龍塘要鑽石山，但係點都好，0730見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有好多朋友，番工番到好攰，但係曠工又會比人炒，又要養妻活兒，真係好想幫下佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日好鍾意番工嘅你同我，會0730去到地鐵，病病地都堅持番工嘅我地緊係要帶口罩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千其唔好跌嘢落個gap，如果跌左就一定要㩒緊急制<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEuMwwn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEuMwwn.png&h=af670ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋記住通知職員幫拖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uL70p8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uL70p8.png&h=c7c21535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟相係喺九龍塘影，無論往黃埔定調景嶺，緊急制都會對住<br />\n1-4同1-5中間<br />\n4-1<br />\n6-1<br />\n8-1<br />\n四個車門<br />\n<br />\n仲有病病地都要番工嘅我地，暈都無可避免，記得見到有人暈就要搵車箱嘅緊急制<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，不分化，不割席，不流血，不被捕！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cdaea1ab36034a1fa236ab80eb94a97da31a4804","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":38,"dislike":72,"score":-34,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"仲有想大家投個票，聽日0730去邊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九龍塘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鑽石山"},{"pid":"f7097ee7d64f3755ec4de602146d65c77b05bf7d","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"1cda31399588b5e51a158b3e87110107f62a16d2","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1544e22f9410b520ab4874d28c8f24c31d96366f","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"不如討論下點解要鑽石山"},{"pid":"89e3662dea462d3cce38d2a30c323ad68b677d5c","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d6c664c4ef42e753b66710d031284d7dbf4f5570","tid":1407061,"uid":92882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"聽朝要單拖自己黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820acd17420c176ea9e23b30eb25e0b58f8cfbc5","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUwi7fE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUwi7fE.png&h=0c444c01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRZMwHk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRZMwHk.png&h=cc3f7181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩個都有圖，討論下投下票"},{"pid":"7ed0112cb13028c6365c68053327eaf6b7a26496","tid":1407061,"uid":155354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"九龍塘核心轉車區<br />\n鑽石山只係觀塘線上其中一個站<br />\n理論上就9龍塘會影響大啲"},{"pid":"5633e2965382b2dfd76759a16d83709828c4536c","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6c664c4ef42e753b66710d031284d7dbf4f5570","tid":1407061,"uid":92882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"聽朝要單拖自己黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"唔驚，番工緊係單拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會有同路人，要有共識"},{"pid":"17431493ef4c160