0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b2f3a890f8600e44d005f601797032ec8e4e39e","tid":1407061,"uid":143580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"我都單拖！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f7a275bf50294aee3d67b10dd02b973763b4b3","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"亦可參考<br />\n你地仲有好多野可以做<br />\n你地係要令車長番左工，但又開唔到工，先可以令佢地罷到工。<br />\n例如露天段，高壓線係比電架列車行，如果唔小心跌野落高壓線，就會無電供應開唔到車。<br />\n車門開啟果時跌發夾／原子筆落空隙，成效一定大過阻礙車門關上，做完又唔會有人知，又唔會比人屌。<br />\n因為就算車長罷工，佢地仲有TCI可以繼續開車，同埋港鐵會有接駁巴士車港奴走。<br />\n<br />\n［突發］8月5號車長大罷工！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb0fdb725a6eb68d205992b03a86bccce63fdab7","tid":1407061,"uid":298237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"點解要鑽石山<br />\n唔係黃大仙 順手係龍翔道發夢"},{"pid":"ffff42be3d574b2221c9969c26a61131551aa37b","tid":1407061,"uid":108584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"上次塞鐵唔係講左話大站狗鐵有曬對應措施同埋好似兜細圈咩？"},{"pid":"c3673b6c8a5b3072f53083aaf6943cf082d10a0d","tid":1407061,"uid":103235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:0