mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715e5ca7253ba79df1a3098f9012464786b86666","tid":1407061,"uid":88577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"好多人要早出門口，最好7點開波"},{"pid":"04f378a205dbc83aa4ce3b8f4c75f201b8f3f7ee","tid":1407061,"uid":92882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21d1b5f588e2db60ebc83b287643ac302369ffc","tid":1407061,"uid":161436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6c664c4ef42e753b66710d031284d7dbf4f5570","tid":1407061,"uid":92882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"聽朝要單拖自己黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:09:53.000Z","msg":"Me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fb2a71569bb760b0f4d9c62f84b0037bceabd1","tid":1407061,"uid":221206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f1f6765381bc9b2153df9061a1f86a16de9297c","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"雖然小弟唔明點解唔要九龍塘要鑽石山，但係點都好，0730見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有好多朋友，番工番到好攰，但係曠工又會比人炒，又要養妻活兒，真係好想幫下佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日好鍾意番工嘅你同我，會0730去到地鐵，病病地都堅持番工嘅我地緊係要帶口罩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千其唔好跌嘢落個gap，如果跌左就一定要㩒緊急制<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEuMwwn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEuMwwn.png&h=af670ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋記住通知職員幫拖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uL70p8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uL70p8.png&h=c7c21535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟相係喺九龍塘影，無論往黃埔定調景嶺，緊急制都會對住<br />\n1-4同1-5中間<br />\n4-1<br />\n6-1<br />\n8-1<br />\n四個車門<br />\n<br />\n仲有病病地都要番工嘅我地，暈都無可避免，記得見到有人暈就要搵車箱嘅緊急制<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，不分化，不割席，不流血，不被捕！</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"求教暈應該係開車前暈定係開咗車暈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acf2bc0e70159da37709ad85726afd38ea5f574","tid":1407061,"uid":298237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"389e979a0efdb537eb900b49ec8708dfe5cfd2c6","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c108583e8a43a96af692a40be5cfd96725ce299a","tid":1407061,"uid":298237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053e6a7ce6ba3a9a6b269262f4e73b161df2a447","tid":1407061,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"九龍灣牛頭角觀塘一路落講緊幾十萬打工仔<br />\n黃大仙/鑽石山KO左佢地就自然被罷工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"所以先係黃大仙<br />\n龍翔道一塞  堆258/259/268/269開唔到車大西北好多返觀塘既就返唔到<br />\n又可以順路去搭地鐵遊下車可"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係遊車河，係集中一個站，唔比佢開車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"唔俾佢開車咁理應唔係咩站做都得到?<br />\n黃大仙會唔會緊要過鑽石山<br />\n龍翔道地鐵可以同時做  <br />\n順手殺埋慈雲山上面落黎既"},{"pid":"85888fb558d578fcabe7c593f2ae9921d06d7c46","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6fb2a71569bb760b0f4d9c62f84b0037bceabd1","tid":1407061,"uid":221206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f1f6765381bc9b2153df9061a1f86a16de9297c","tid":1407061,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:44:13.